entries.femaleVariant: H-hey man. G-gonna need a few more of your wheezers.
An' I'm gonna need some corp data.
Wh-what? What're you...? No. No, man, I can't.... Please. I got the eddies right here, like always.
Choom, please. I'm beggin' ya. Jesus, look at me.
Shakes're just gonna get worse. You think you're the only 'Saka gonk who buys from us?
All-- all right. Fuck it, fine! Just gimme – gimme the wheezers.
We know where you live, we know where your kids go to school, we know you're slottin' Julia. Now get the fuck outta my sight.
